An excellent opportunity for an experienced and career minded individual to join our dynamic Sales Team - and to establish a rewarding career with the fastest growing hotel company, The Carlson Rezidor Hotel Group.
Main  Scope / Purpose:
The purpose of this role is to maximize hotel revenue by negotiating and securing profitable rooms business with a special focus on leisure market and coordinating the execution of such leads with other departments in accordance with the sales business plan; and deepen existing relationship with clients through effective communication using technology and optimising on marketing activities and guest service etiquettes.
The ideal candidate should have at least; • 2 years experience in Sales with a luxury hotel in Dubai, with proven track record / achievements in leisure market
• Excellent communication skills and English language ability; preferably bilingual
• Excellent interpersonal skills
• Sales and service oriented
• Ability to explain complex information clearly and simply
• Ability to analyze and research information
• Commmercial minded and be able to easily build rapport with guests.
• Customer-focussed and understands importance of service delivery excellence.
• Highly driven and self motivated
• Valid UAE Driving Licence
If you are efficient, organized and dynamic , the above requirements match your experience and you are open to work with a progressive Sales & Marketing team, then we are looking forward to receiving your updated CV including photo.
